profile:
ProHanging prides itself as being a high quality option for any household hanging service. Understanding the need to create a unique space means paying attention to detail and listening to the homeowner. Since 2006, ProHanging has been hanging Art, Mirrors, Picture Frames, TV's (TV installations), Blinds, and Specialty items in homes, condos and various institutions throughout the GTA.

You don't pay unless you are 100% satisfied with our service. That's a promise!

Art and Picture hanging is our specialty. We started our organization based on these services and continue to provide a top-notch customer satisfaction service at its finest terms.

We do not provide Electrical work.

Services Include: 

Mounting Service 
*Hanging artwork and sentimental pieces is more than just hammering a nail on the wall, it’s an Art on its own. We inspect all artwork to be safely hung on a particular wall, making sure that artwork will last a lifetime. 
*Mirrors Hanging and Installations 
*Decorative Items Installations
*Window Coverings 
*Blinds Hanging
*Bathroom Accessories Hanging
*Flat Screen TVs Mounting

Give us a call for a quote today and get it installed the right way.

profile:
Hi, My name is Barbara. I'm thrilled to announce that I'm celebrating 18 years of Decorating & Designing.

Barbara Nyke Interiors & Design is a residential interior design & decorating studio.  We design custom kitchens, baths and décor for busy professionals primarily in: Toronto, North York, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Caledon, Vaughan, Richmond Hill, The Beach and Scarborough.  For projects located elsewhere, we are delighted to take our designs beyond the GTA.

Here's an article about "Why You Need to Hire a Kitchen Designer" - I'm the featured kitchen designer in the article.. Please copy & paste: https://blog.homestars.com/expert-opinion-why-need-kitchen-designer/

To get your project started, book a 2-hr kitchen design consultation with me.  I'll give you a comprehensive set of preliminary design recommendations including space planning, how to maximize counter space, cabinetry design, estimated project costs and more. Then we're ready for Step 2 of the NIKKA DESIGN process.

--------------

Barbara was a guest designer on "The Property Brothers" TV show.
 
I helped to redesign and renovate the entire main floor of a suburban 1960s home that included: the foyer, dining room, living room, kitchen and family room. Please see our Gallery for some photos.
 
"We design exceptional spaces. Our desire is to serve our valued and respected clientele by transforming how you live and work.  We rely on experience, expertise and impeccable integrity to complete projects on time, on budget and with stunning results".

profile:
House Letter Signs is here to personalize the look of your house with our custom house addresses. We design, manufacture and install your custom house address using our high quality materials and professional craftsmanship. Our products for Toronto are $220 for matte, or $260 for glossy + HST. This price includes installation, and there may be an additional cost for installation dependent on the location of the required services. We provide: House Signs, Custom Scripts, Home Addresses, Cursive Fonts, House Numbers, Letters Sign and Cursive Writing. 

We are now offering brand new products and finishes! We offer Brushed gold, brushed silver, chrome, and bronze. 

***

Our products are made from 1/2" black or white PVC (matte finish), or 1/4” black acrylic (glossy). Our manufacturing turnaround time is 2-3 business days, with installations occurring only on the weekends. To start your free design consultation, please send us a picture of the front of your house, and provide us with your address. Our design team will gladly work with you.

Please view more reviews at http://www.facebook.com/houselettersigns

If you have any additional questions or would like to place an order. please email us at houselettersigns@gmail.com or call us at 905-604-3130.

profile:
Welcome to Infinite Prosperity! My name is Katalin and I'll be your personal design specialist. Please have a look at my profile and if you think I'm the perfect designer for your upcoming project, let's chat.

What I “bring to the table” that is unique and exclusive.

I believe that design & decor is more than just beautifying your immediate surroundings with the latest "trends". My unique approach is detail-oriented, which includes taking into account the needs and personalities of everyone living in your space(s). Below are just some of the things I take into consideration before I begin any project:

    -Incorporate colours best suited to the personalities of everyone in your home
    -What textures would work best
    -Include the perfect elements
    -Consider what the space will be used for and plan accordingly
    -How I can incorporate memories and sentimental pieces to your space
    -How I can bring in fresh energy to create harmony and balance for your space

I can accomplish this by using different techniques which can be as simple as changing paint colours all the way up to adding the appropriate window treatments, reupholstering your current pieces and choosing new pieces to enhance any space in your home, whether it's your family room, master bedroom to create more passion or your home office to enhance your productivity. No job is too big or small.

The most important thing to me is creating a warm and inviting space for you and your family, it's that simple. It's all about YOU!

Kindest Wishes,

Katalin
products:
All of the products are fully customized to each individuals needs and desires.

services:
Whether it is your home or professional space, our unique approach is highly detail-oriented, considering, and incorporating colours, textures, elements into the design, that is specifically chosen for your individual needs and desires. 

Whether it is choosing a paint color for your home office,  selecting the appropriate window treatment for your bedroom, reupholstering an old sentimental piece of furniture for your family room, or offering Feng Shui consultation to bring in fresh energy, it is all necessary for shaping harmony and balance in both your private and professional life. 

We are proud to work with small, local, highly skilled craftsmen, where each project is treated equally with a priority, regardless of how big or small the job is. 

You are treated more than just a "number". We believe that no job is too small! Our prices are budget-sensitive offering environmentally conscious suggestions with a sensible approach. 

We are dedicated to finding you the ultimate options. We offer a white-glove pick-up & delivery service and basic set-up as promised.

profile:
If You Are Reading These Words, You Are At An Interior Design Crossroad.
You might know what you want, but not how to achieve it, or you might not have the slightest idea where to start… whichever it is, we will work together to create and evoke the look of your home and sanctuary.

Home décor and design are big parts of what makes our eyes rest at the end of the day, our souls happy, and our minds at peace. We will bring to light the potential of your space,  and together make sure that every time you walk into your home, there is a wonderful and exhilarating feeling that wraps around and brings smiles and warm feelings to heart.

At LookEvoke, we bring new ideas and concepts, always on the look for a unique approach for the space. Our philosophy is pretty simple; relaxed sophistication.
